CERTIFICATE OF ACCOMPLISHMENT
This is a sample Blockcerts certficiate produced by Credentia

This is to certify that Brian Veritas, having complied with the laws of the State of New Mexico regulating the practice of Public Accountancy, is hereby authorized to perform services as a Certified Public Accountant as prescribed in the 1999 Public Accountancy Act. This active certificate is in good standing.

The recipient is authorized to perform the following services: accounting and book keeping, financial statements, analysis and compilation, filing and resolution of tax issues, tax planning and projection, new business set-up and consulting, company payroll, and ITIN and notary services.
